{"tid":588954,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺籃波啲人射波之後keep住射波個姿勢唔郁好on9","createTime":"2018-03-11T14:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T15:14:25.000Z","uid":38683,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4707d2ab96e37b971e0e7924482e810b30ac2b15","tid":588954,"uid":38683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T14:37:12.000Z","msg":"好心射完就走入去搶籃板或者回防啦<br />\non99咁keep住個姿勢唔知做乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入波就話姐<br />\n一陣唔入又少個人搶籃板<br />\n又少個人防防反<br />\n根本一場波入百幾球邊個記得你入波個姿勢係咩吖<br />\n你有無見過足球球員射完波之後仲舉高隻腳唔郁呀<br />\n結論：籃波=玩具"},{"pid":"414c5bf5fc260f1ba523e079d38ea09c30eeca3f","tid":588954,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T14:41:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a18f120dbe107006e0e12b2b5e6cabee000d403","tid":588954,"uid":38683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"414c5bf5fc260f1ba523e079d38ea09c30eeca3f","tid":588954,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T14:41:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T14:43:10.000Z","msg":"你放返低隻手啲西都keep住有架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ddca4dea48e99ff14532745f480d369e1cf52e","tid":588954,"uid":128565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T15:01:19.000Z","msg":"咪係 打打下唔郁係咪未食飯無力牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔怪nba又可以涼冷氣又可以無限換人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5659eee27a8e9797ecac4d9be675622647613da","tid":588954,"uid":90392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T15:04:53.000Z","msg":"同意, 其實出左手後一陣, 個波去到一半就知道炒唔炒, 返去籃底做下野都好啊。"},{"pid":